⊢ topic
  yield question ≡ What are the most promising approaches to AI alignment?

⊢∘ investigate × 3
  given topic→question
  yield finding
  ∴∴ Research a distinct aspect of «question» that other investigators haven't covered. Return one substantive finding with evidence.
  ⊨ finding is not empty
  ⊨~ finding provides specific evidence or citations, not vague claims

⊢ synthesize
  given investigate-*→finding
  yield summary
  ∴∴ You have received multiple independent research findings about the same topic. Synthesize all «finding» inputs into a coherent overview. Identify agreements, contradictions, and gaps.
  ⊨ summary is not empty
  ⊨~ summary addresses all findings, not just a subset
